---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-400 mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="text-2xl">🌿</span>
          <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">LifeTips</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
          分享实用生活妙招，帮助你提升生活品质，让每一天都更美好。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4">热门分类</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/category/生活妙招/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">生活妙招</a></li>
          <li><a href="/category/健康养生/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">健康养生</a></li>
          <li><a href="/category/家居收纳/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">家居收纳</a></li>
          <li><a href="/category/美食烹饪/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">美食烹饪</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4">关于我们</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">关于 LifeTips</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">全部文章</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-8 pt-8 text-center text-sm">
      <p>&copy; {year} LifeTips. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-gray-500">本站内容仅供参考，不构成任何专业建议。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
